=Episode 22=

3
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:30,120
How about I...

4
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:31,550
I...

5
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:41,030
Let me feel Her Highness's pulse.

6
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:47,030
She isn't sick,

7
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:49,640
