for abandoning her mission.

8
00:00:51,110 --> 00:00:52,070
Being punished?

9
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:56,520
Shen Juan's favorability value isn't full,

10
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:58,790
but it is still going up.

11
00:00:58,870 --> 00:01:01,240
So, your mission is still available.

12
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,790
But she totally gave up on killing you.

13
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:06,950
She's certainly being punished.

14
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,710
In the following days,

15
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:09,840
