16
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:12,150
until she dies.

17
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,840
It's so important

18
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,430
and why are you just bringing it up now?

19
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,070
You didn't ask me.

20
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,200
And because the two of you
forcibly changed

21
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,310
