22
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,760
this world

23
00:01:24,070 --> 00:01:25,560
will collapse soon, too.

24
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:41,790
Shaoheng,

25
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,920
I'm here to see Juanjuan.

26
00:01:47,730 --> 00:01:49,940
Did the physicians say what was wrong?

27
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:53,990
She's fine.

28
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:55,760
She's just exhausted

29
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,390
