after a few days' rest.

30
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,240
Glad to hear that.

31
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:02,820
Shaoheng,

32
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:05,460
I'm going to visit the Southside

33
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,540
to get some inspiration for my new novel.

34
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:10,860
With Lian Yue?

35
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:13,700
Yes.

36
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:15,860
Juanjuan said,

37
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:17,780
