51
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:29,420
Then grab my hand tightly.

52
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,460
All right.

53
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,180
I'll go out with you.

54
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:55,500
What are you thinking?

55
00:03:57,620 --> 00:03:58,900
This is where

56
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:00,860
I met you for the first time.

57
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,060
Comet

58
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:07,420
